ding to me it must be a texture of creamy cream custard and had a bubble on the custard without that burnt sugar on top your not gonna eat it. The chocolate cake is for free or a gift since it's my birthday this coming April 22nd that is 2 days from now. The lunch meal is quite affordable with 4 appetizer, the appetizer is delicious as well the main dish. The steak I expect is not that good since I am craving for red meat for Easter Sunday of honoring the life of Jesus by not eating meat in the Holy Week. The drinks is extra plus to end the meal. The service is like a force they serve the appetizer and soup together are filling on the table. And you have to eat fast the soup or other appetizer you will not wanted to eat cold. We tell the waitress take a bit slow that they gonna serve the mean dish soon.  The atmosphere is noisy today. But not surprising for me this is not the first time we dined here. So the service the atmosphere reduce the point. The plates are dirty  and have not wipe the sides of the plates before serving, you cant see it through pictures. The plates have scratch from pots or pans in the kitchen is like you put the food then the garnish that is! it doesn't matter it looks clean or not, the Head Chef doesnt care the cleanliness of each plates. Just advice the management just keep the same service in the Cafe Grazie in Far Eastern Department store. There is more relax the service is not they serving all the food at once. We got suprise as well the Cafe Grazie in Far Eastern have  improve the dining system when serving the food.\",\"time\":1745164939,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"crys tal\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108347919114795581291/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMiO-1ISBqIuQE40cnnz5OqiKRWjWdnxb_mu7Mn8QfoKrsrD5g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"5 months ago\",\"text\":\"The ambiance is perfect—welcoming, cozy, and great for both casual dinners or special occasions. The food was incredibly delicious, and each dish was full of flavor. However, one downside was the BBQ pork ribs. While they were still packed with great flavor, they weren't as tender as I had hoped. Despite that, the taste was still fantastic, and I’d definitely return to enjoy more of their mouthwatering dishes. Highly recommend for a great meal and atmosphere!\",\"time\":1735732262,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Rovie David\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105608763185434893917/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjjyanJAaI_rpNiPk4FAl8lEz2Vc3-k-IFiqjp8opIBEFpXA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 weeks ago\",\"text\":\"Great food and environment the staff are easy to approach the arrangements of the order is good. I will recommend it to my friends. If you are celebrating your birthday they will ask you for free dessert and drinks.\",\"time\":1747326103,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Hannah Shi\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101540560183132274872/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuY_hQX1vi3YtsPvTtMkN6KiFX3VuGNwXyxyyj-Tqn4T_92g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"6 months ago\",\"text\":\"Fried fish—4 star. Light, airy, crispy, with good wasabi sauce. One critique: too little fish in each piece. I ate more fried batter than fish.\\n\\nAngus beef pizza: 3 star. Not flavorful. Good portion beef, but there is no sauce with very little cheese.\\n\\nBeef pasta: 3 star, soaking in sauce, wilted garnishes. Sauce taste like its out of the can.\\n\\nPotato au gratin 5star. Raw egg inside was a pleasant surprise. Boyfriend is western, thinks it tastes just like home.\\n\\nService: Servers do okay job. Did not seem to care very much they took a while to get our order, probably because we came at the final hour.\\n\\nAtmosphere: top notch. Easy 5 star.\",\"time\":1731291635,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"廖欣怡\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115251983469657216846/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV__CSkdkdUfO_3v-bnVaRnNjuj6hp6hgN6me0qwuvH4-Sf7jN0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 months ago\",\"text\":\"Good price for a set meal, the staff is very helpful ☺️\",\"time\":1737637020,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNTJXMC9DeGF8q6KkXY6ZDjkfnccyDYyH8N7tCBqm5ETcwydLN_tSAhiYsQevjEb6BVkmNtZuVoHhuBBairuCfVg1lUIXwpN-5zuixfCW-_179M10yNWn50K5JjV4lim6Toc89t3uNuoWgaYhuFnAwP7RKiHgyTvi0zJj8Ea7OiYPJh8_Ijg5iaqqr2shENIdyZvZcIB2x14jdNk96LhjYccSyRLzNizVOUV2hWhs5XKTpoY6Ww8whrN9ago6B2ErbIBvBOfJuFx9q4JpeHQrW14WkMYi9tnrwJmG-1Ka88ozhND_z15TzbfbqEayjGhWWjSU6RTAApoecN_x0KkMjFRxMrBgo1uvUxck20vre-OtKWmUuzn6UtUKEI65zEfXaF4cAzEqJxNt8QMM7Vr9yXAHJ4UyQOz4qeLPrOysbbVzk2HW4x7dNnbM8-9okCuUAwH8mPn8cB5-Kw8TmVbeXLvvb7Wm4oNZqTgGKffX5V0IXlDR4P5DdAx_m2aI_G5g0yyPQCoWFIXIhzuYJVCDfXQLoeeU08jfbDzqFdBF1Eq8NFAZvT7s165HZho1Njk2x39TS11vVnPSk6IwnsMmMogzuxYUa3mBK1FE4eqQCWHM4X6FeBI25AZgQUZPmBg5RPpSg\",\"AXQCQNQoE0aZ7_YLHoAkb-66SFWWkyM4APB0Oa9NA4NmKVe1d5m0vnTD3h91rd9qBIgJTDkO4439OpXtf_Mjs2x2dCGUzVZMn2aRp7TT6_twuzMAbKPaODybc58dPVRcra5sGhnkluUOmVolTZPhMTCjAsS1cOcZl9VMVCJ5qJsPaTAgQzftwOxl72eY2-tHP8CfaIC98calVYCtkOeFMB5fbU0jidnrQ-8N7xyPqmxlzavINIT7c2dT2_KH-9u0sP9As389DNDWWd9zSacUa-LwYyKoGU3MxG9fRYQUrl8dmNTaB4KLotSC_HIgjvE4lsSgBlXWUS41aC6XVhv8NYxbCdC3zo_VM-bZ6NXfVnBPXhM0MdyLQQviVlavGX5NjP2dUj4qeXWdrd8nsgiGeiAdv73Q2DXorX4yk_X_v6Det2A-EtKkFFEn3wPLql_dY4mlWmFKMqhkqlXRo6V4j9xPmLZ1XHQ4opxZmqzdYeijhMWE1HO1CeGWhnxcAiNO7pmGkH723Hyrvx8ZfZeF-NjQUYmm6onqtwyxosphSu7x5u7RQ8nhGSyHjFSabQGnYGnE0iDmYF28JGsPQA9VliljmS0n-gqpJsGC06bSGp7jfPbMLpSwcWOStiYbax1YZFMK6cchVJG4\",\"AXQCQNREECuCqvjL6VSqxun2b0tiOo13PGt4V1okxGDSYmdbNLPCBGoIl7FUWXl6I8