:{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":15,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":17,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}}],\"rating\":4.4,\"reviews\":[{\"author_name\":\"Bob Cook\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113314347498798056711/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnVtt9YJqcF1nKU0HYeFRnAskfJtzUZjJ7wzw1xsyOyTpVQFIGmQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 months ago\",\"text\":\"This is always a great place to eat delicious Italian food with attentive service. I absolutely love their salmon salad, bread and tiramisu. On a cold day I recommend their slow cooked beef.\\n\\nPizzas are light and flavorful with a slightly chewy crust . Do have a look at their lunch menu as they often try out new or more adventurous dishes on  it.  Be aware that this place gets busy even during the week at lunchtimes so I would recommend booking.\",\"time\":1741086526,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Brendan Scott\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114941291296691114552/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKIOGLi-Dqwdak7P3t7ljkEXxdpDp__WqUIydH9cnAARX0vBHn=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"6 years ago\",\"text\":\"The food here is pretty good. I would have to agree with everyone else that the breadsticks are very delicious and definitely worth getting. It’s good bread fresh out of the oven and they give you a great dipping sauce for it. The soup is better than most places, as well. Salad was delicious! Everything we had here was good. Original pizza, beef lasagna, and Carbonara pasta were all good. Worth coming here if you’re in the area.\",\"time\":1529904604,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Salina Kuo\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106337605422456895854/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_1nvRPa0uhXEFK-DLrmdc-OzRhu-h9AbPiW7efkfVyN5Y7YSK=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"5 years ago\",\"text\":\"My experience with Friendy has been consistently exceptional. They serve top-notch Italian food, with the spinach ravioli and tiramisu being my favorite. I’ve only tried their pizza once, but I remember it being delicious as well. Cannot recommend enough if you’re craving for ravioli in Hsinchu.\",\"time\":1561442409,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Johanny\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110468272088921547032/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGbXq_fx9yfLXBk9MX6pjT8WB6FchSVNbT7JkSmbZXXwCphZfVfQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 years ago\",\"text\":\"This is my favorite Italian restaurant in Taiwan! They have the best tiramisu and lasagna I have tasted here in tw. They have straight out of the oven delicious bread, great pizza, the smoked salmon pasta is my favorite, and the antipasti are amazing (the mushrooms and beef more than the eggplant). Moreover, the service is always good and the price is fair.\",\"time\":1621555993,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Diego Alejandro Graneros\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108469035978678131149/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4cmYpwR5uxrKbSyG6upDD-0t--083t9k0WisVLUH0R2cVl290lA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 years ago\",\"text\":\"The best pizza and pasta i tried in Hsinchu. Taste like in Italy or Argentina. Dessert are delicious too. The 2 girls working there give an excellent service. Prices are fair. They play latin-hispanic music.\",\"time\":1680470606,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNRSO9cpr-Q9vWyzEe2ZCzra6Gzk1iRCKdvQ1b